Per-device, per-site vehicle comparisons

The following graph gives insight into how the vehicles compare on the sites in the test corpus. Here we see Chrome 73 and Fenix 68 ARM generally competing well, with Chrome 73 having a slight edge.

The web.de URL appears to be an outlier: perhaps a bad recording explains the aberrant measurements.

If we remove web.de and plot the median page load times, we can clearly see that Fenix 68 ARM is mostly lagging Chrome 73.
